data.message:
My friend, Carolyn Pruitt Anderson, can only see a few posts on my facebook page, Shirley Coombs Harris. We are best friends, and she is quite aggravated about it. She only sees a few posts from way back. Please send me a message telling me why, or better yet, PLEASE CORRECT THE PROBLEM, AND NOTIFY ME. Thank you.
9/26/15
Here is the note I got from her this morning:Looks like to me I don't see ANYTHING you, yourself, posted since july 16... all before that was posted to your page by me or someone else.
PLEASE FIX THIS!!!
